l participation Is it possible to do object programming in {your favorite programming language}? The conscious use of abstraction is very well understood in the programming world. Investigation is needed for better use of abstraction in information modeling. One of the major issues here is how to describe information (data + behavior) independently of how it is stored or used. Among the questions to be addressed:. How can you represent catalogs of data elements and encyclopedic resources for information management with regard to representation of behavior?